Text.Value: Where are you from?
Brought to Gur hunter camp... Cazador found them... took me...
Dead... abandoned... Cazador found me... brought me back...
What were you planning to do as a Vampire Lord?
Leave.
Met people... Talked. Flirted. Lured back for my master...
What was your profession?
Not a question... but good...
Two hundred years?... hard to remember...
Where I can find Cazador?
Some... but never to feed... only brought master living victims...
Rule this place... finally be free...
Cazador Szarr... ancient vampire... bastard...
What happened to you?
Baldur's Gate...
Astarion... vampire spawn...
Have many people have you killed?
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*
Who are you?
Who was your master?
Taken by mind flayers... killed after crash...
Cazador's dead. I just wanted you to know.
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
How did you end up in the ritual?
How old are you?
In Baldur's Gate... his palace...
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis:
SwD with Astarion.
Some questions are unlocked as we learn more about Astarion.
